  "description": "<p><strong>Roles & Responsibilities</strong></p><p>· Maintain neatness and general cleanliness of the store.</p><p>. Wipe clean desks, partitions, glass doors and all table tops</p><p>· Maintenance of pantry including displaying, organising and replenishing pantry items.</p><p>· Prepare beverages and desserts for customers.</p><p>· Perform other ad-hoc duties, as and when required.</p><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><p>· Working Location: Orchard</p><p>· 5 days work week (Off on Saturday, Sunday and Public Holiday)</p><p>· Working Hours: Mon to Fri- 11.00am to 2.00pm (3 hours per day)</p><p>· Attire: Company T-shirt (will be provided)</p><p>· Minimum 1 to 2 years of working experience in cleaning services</p>",
